snippet.title: Google Stitch 4.0 (Upgraded): Google's Gemini-3 & Nano Banana Pro Designer is ACTUALLY INSANE!
snippet.description:
Visit Augment Code: https://www.augmentcode.com/

In this video, I'll be breaking down the relentless updates from Google regarding the Gemini ecosystem and Stitch. They just dropped the hilariously named Nano Banana Pro model and a massive integration with AI Studio that changes how we design and build software.
